Class Filopart

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.gurdon.Filopart

  • public class Filopart
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a 2-dimensional filopodium. Stores Rois, time and part indices, coordinates and statistics.
    Author:
    Richard Butler

        pixW - The calibrated pixel width
        t - The timepoint that this process exists at

        a - The process area in units^2
        meanB - The base mean intensity
        meanP - The process mean intensity

        meanThT - The thresholded mean intensity
        sigma - The Gaussian sigma value used to detect this process
